<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Team Building Help</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/53/Pok%C3%A9_Ball_icon.svg">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-600 border-8 border-red-600 shadow-xl w-full h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-6">
    <nav class="absolute top-6 left-4">
        <a
          href="/dash"
          class="bg-red-600 text-white font-mono text-lg px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-red-800 shadow-lg hover:bg-red-500 hover:border-red-700"
        >
          Return to Dashboard
        </a>
      </nav>

    <div class=" max-w-4xl flex items-center justify-between">
        <!-- Left Section: Title, Text, Buttons -->
        <div class="w-[70%] flex flex-col items-center">
            <!-- Title -->
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                <img src="/images/Team-Building-Help-1-28-2025.png" alt="teambuildinghelp" class="w-[400px] md:w-[800px]">
              </div>

            <!-- Subtitle -->
            <h2 class="text-lg text-white font-semibold mt-4 mb-3">
                Need help getting into team building?
            </h2>

            <!-- Description -->
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed px-6">
                Pokémon team building can be very challenging to get into. What Pokémon are good? 
                How should I design a team? We took the liberty of adding some resources for you 
                to learn from. The first two links are for the main competitive Pokémon companies, 
                while the others are experienced YouTubers who provide insights into team building 
                from different perspectives.
            </p>

            <!-- Guide Buttons -->
            <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2">
                <a href="#" class="bg-[#7fd6dc] text-white font-mono text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#6fc2c7]">
                    Smogon Guide
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="bg-[#e04d40] text-white font-mono text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#cc4539]">
                    VGC Guide
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- YouTube Links -->
            <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                <a href="#" class="bg-[#6a22cc] text-white font-mono text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#5a1db5]">
                    CybertronVGC
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="bg-[#5f8cf7] text-white font-mono text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#4e7add]">
                    pokeaimMD
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="bg-[#af8cf7] text-white font-mono text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#9a79e5]">
                    WolfyVGC
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Section: Character Image -->
        <div class="flex justify-end">
            <img src="/images/n-pokemon.gif" 
                 alt="N Character" class="lg:w-52">
        </div>
    </div>

